Description: I18NCode for How do we protect your information
Default_Translation (en-en):
We have taken all steps necessary to protect the information in our systems. We utilize encryption (for communication and storage) and security software to safeguard the confidentiality of personal information we process from unauthorized access or disclosure and accidental loss, alteration or destruction. We also perform regular tests to our infrastructure and systems in order to identify security vulnerabilities.

If you have access to Reporting2You website, remember that your account is protected in part by your password. It is important that you protect and maintain your account security and that you tell us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.
Target_Translation (de-de): Wir haben alle notwendigen Schritte unternommen, um die Informationen in unseren Systemen zu schützen.

Description: I18NCode for How long will your information be held
Default_Translation (en-en): Your information will be kept in our system while you are a BNI Member, Director or Ambassador and up to 2 years after the termination of this relationship.
Target_Translation (de-de): Ihre Daten werden in unserem System gespeichert, solange Sie BNI-Mitglied, Direktor oder Botschafter sind und bis zu zwei Jahre nach Beendigung dieser Beziehung.

Description: I18NCode for What are your rights
Default_Translation (en-en):
You have the right to access your data and that your personal data is always kept up to date. Also, you have the right to ask for us to erase all your data if you think this is in your best interest. Additionally, you have the right to withdraw your consent, in which case we will stop processing your data, meaning that your name will not be visible at any report nor at reporting2you website.

To exercise any of your rights, you may contact our Data Protection Officer, identified in the end of this policy.
Target_Translation (de-de): Sie haben das Recht, auf Ihre Daten zuzugreifen und sicherzustellen, dass Ihre personenbezogenen Daten stets auf dem neuesten Stand gehalten werden.

Description: I18NCode for Answer What information do we collect about you
Default_Translation (en-en):
To be able to provide our services, we download from BNI Connect the following information about you:

  • First and Last Name, Company Name, Profession, Email, Telephones, BNI Role, Join Date, Renewal Date, weekly PALMS records, Membership activity and Training Attendance (if applicable in your region or chapter).
  • If you have access to the Reporting2You website (only BNI Directors or authorized personnel), we also collect, by automatic means and through the use of the Reporting2You website, the following information: Cookies (with your authorization on the website) and Analytics (with IP anonymization).
Target_Translation (de-de): Um unsere Dienste anbieten zu können, laden wir von BNI Connect die folgenden Informationen über Sie herunter:

Description: I18NCode for What is our legal basis for processing your personal data
Default_Translation (en-en): We have a formal agreement with the your BNI Franchisee, which authorizes us to collect your data from BNI Connect. We process data with your consent under Article 6 1(a) of the General Data Protection Regulation.
Target_Translation (de-de): Wir haben eine formelle Vereinbarung mit Ihrem BNI-Franchisenehmer, die uns ermächtigt, Ihre Daten von BNI Connect zu erfassen.

Description: i18NCode for Answer Who Are We
Default_Translation (en-en): DeepEye is the organization that develops and maintains the Reporting2You application and platform, aimed at giving you tools to achieve high performance and better results from your BNI membership by preparing and sending you reports that help you take decisions and actions to succeed. We have our office established in Portugal.
Target_Translation (de-de): DeepEye ist die Organisation, die die Anwendung und Plattform Reporting2You entwickelt und pflegt. Ziel ist es, Ihnen Tools an die Hand zu geben, mit denen Sie mit Ihrer BNI-Mitgliedschaft eine hohe Leistung und bessere Ergebnisse erzielen können, indem Berichte erstellt und versendet werden, die Ihnen dabei helfen, Entscheidungen zu treffen und Maßnahmen zu ergreifen, um erfolgreich zu sein.

Description: I18NCode for Who receives your information

Target_Translation (de-de): Nur Sie, Mitglieder Ihres Chapters, BNI-Direktoren oder autorisierte Mitarbeiter des Franchisenehmers können Berichte mit Ihren persönlichen Daten erhalten.

Description: I18NCode for What is a Cookie
Default_Translation (en-en): A cookie is a piece of information placed on the hard drive of Internet users by the server of the site they visit. It contains several pieces of data: the name of the server which installed it, an identifier in the form of a unique number, and possibly an expiry date. This information is sometimes stored on the computer in a simple text file that a server accesses to read and save pieces of information. The Reporting2You uses cookies whose purpose is to facilitate navigation on the site, to execute the service provided by DeepEye, to measure the site’s audience or to allow pages on the site to be shared.
Target_Translation (de-de): Ein Cookie ist eine Information, die vom Server der von ihnen besuchten Website auf der Festplatte des Internetnutzers abgelegt wird.

Description: I18NCode for Back To Login Page

Default_Translation (en-en):
• Entry and Exit of Members during the previous month can only take place by 16:00 of the second working day of each month, as the information which will form the basis for the monthly calculation shall be downloaded at the end of that day;
  • Monthly PALMS reports should be entered by the second working day of each month as Member Traffic Lights will be calculated at the end of that day;
  • PALMS reports should be entered during the 48h following the meeting and cannot be more than 4 weeks late, as they will not be considered by Reporting2You;
  • Members should not be allowed to change their names and if this happens, a notification should be sent to info@reporting2you.com ;
  • Groups should not be allowed to change their names and if this happens, a notification should be sent to info@reporting2you.com ;
  • All Groups should have a Director Consultant and Area Director on BNI Connect
  • In order to use the Core Group report as soon as the director enters the PALMS report on BNI Connect, an e-mail should be sent to info@reporting2you.com ;
  • Regions using Group goals will have a more detailed weekly report for Leadership Teams, as it will contain the evolution of the 8 Key Success Factors over the last two months and the current month;
  • Monthly Reports shall be calculated at the end of the second working day of each month;
  • Leadership Teams should be up to date by 16:00 of the second working day of April and October. If any changes occur, a notification should be sent to info@reporting2you.com ;
  • If you want to stop receiving email with the reports, you need to uncheck the “Send emails” at “Regional Administration->Regional Settings->The Region” menu at reporting2you.com;
  • You should use “Regional Administration->Regional Settings->Reports” menu to set who receives each report;
  • You must write the word “substitution” in the drop notes, if the drop reason is really for substitute the member.

Default_Translation (en-en):
This is a weekly report that usually is sent to each Leadership Team every Monday 9PM.
The goal is to give information that President (Chapter Director in England), Vice-President and Secretary/Treasurer usually needs to dig on several BNIConnect reports to run their role.
With this report, the President can easily select the meeting stimulant or his final words to the meeting.
The Vice-President can understand who needs special attention and work with his coordinators to improve member performance.
The Events Coordinator understands who is not attending training and needs special motivational speech to do it.
Target_Translation (de-de): Hierbei handelt es sich um einen wöchentlichen Bericht, der normalerweise jeden Montag um 21:00 Uhr an jedes Führungsteam gesendet wird.
